description: Supports spells, or attacks that use bows or wands. Instead of using that skill, you will throw a trap that will use the skill for you when an enemy walks near it. Traps cannot use channelling skills.

mods.text: Supported Skills have % increased Trap Throwing Speed
Supported Skills have % increased Trap Trigger Area of Effect

mods: Supported Skills have (0–19)% increased Trap Throwing Speed
Supported Skills deal (0–38)% increased Trap Damage
Supported Attack Skills cannot be used with Melee Weapons
name: Trap Support
